      • MultipleChoice

        public MultipleChoice(javafx.scene.Group nGroup,
              float xStart,
              float yStart,
              java.util.ArrayList<Answer> answers,
              MultipleChoiceObject.MultiChoiceType nType,
              MultipleChoiceObject.Orientation nOrientation,
              boolean nRetry,
              int nMarks)
        Constructor method to create multiple choice object
        Parameters:
        nGroup - A group this object will be added to
        xStart - X-coordinate of the top left corner multiple choice in pixels
        yStart - Y-coordinate of the top left corner multiple choice in pixels
        answers - List of correct answers
        nType - Type of multiple choice. E.g. drop down, radio..
        nOrientation - Vertical/horizontal orientation of the object
        nRetry - Enable/disable retry after wrong attempt
        nMarks - Marks for correct answer
